# Tremor Tile — sdkconfig.defaults
# Pico SDK configuration defaults

# This file is used by the Pico SDK build system.
# Since RP2040 uses Pico SDK (not ESP-IDF), most configuration
# is done in CMakeLists.txt rather than sdkconfig.

# Pico SDK defaults for this project:
# - USB CDC for console output (field service)
# - UART0 disabled (pins used for other peripherals)
# - CPU frequency: 133 MHz (default, sufficient for FFT)
# - Flash size: 16MB (W25Q128)

# Override CPU frequency if needed for FFT performance:
# set(PICO_DEFAULT_CLOCK_FREQ_KHZ 266000)  # 266 MHz overclock

# Note: Pico SDK uses CMake configuration, not Kconfig like ESP-IDF.
# See CMakeLists.txt for all build configuration.